Trustmark says names Hickson president / CEO . Trustmark Corp said on Tuesday that it named Richard Hickson president and chief executive , succeeding Frank Day , who stepped down for health reasons . Trustmark said Hickson will also assume the post of chief executive of its Trustmark National Bank unit . It said Day remains chairman of both Trustmark and Trustmark National Bank . It said Hickson , 52 , has served since 1995 as president and chief operating officer of SouthTrust Bank of Georgia NA , a unit of SouthTrust Corp . 
